{
  "id": "adv_event_2405_01_01",
  "title": "BIG4への\n道のり",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ、長かったライブツアーも\n今日で無事おしまいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew‚ our long live tour\nis finally over today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.8391605377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.0333330154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。今回のツアーも\n最終日まで誰も怪我なく完走出来て、良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone. I’m glad we were able to\ncomplete this tour without anyone getting injured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333330154,
      "endTime": 13.739160537699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "どの会場でもいいパフォーマンスが出来たし\nみんなも、よく頑張ってくれたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We gave good performances at all the venues‚\nand you all worked hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9333330154,
      "endTime": 19.4058269501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5999994278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～。莉央さん、何言ってるんですか～？\nそんな控えめな賛辞では全然足りませーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~ Rio-san‚ what are you saying?\nThat kind of reserved compliment isn’t nearly enough~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5999994278,
      "endTime": 26.9419720649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1361445427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさん、すっごい盛り上がってましたし\nアンコールなんて全員総立ちでしたからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans were super hyped up‚\nand during the encore‚ everyone was standing up~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1361445427,
      "endTime": 34.1830379486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3772104263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもみたいに「私達のライブに空席はいらないわ」\n「おーほほほ！」って高笑いして下さいよ。ほら～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why don’t you laugh haughtily like you always do and say‚\n“We don’t need empty seats at our lives. O~hohoho!”. Come on~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3772104263,
      "endTime": 43.3841720581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.5783445358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "私はそんなキャラじゃないわよ\nまったく、貴方はいつもいつも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not that kind of character.\nHonestly‚ you always…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5783445358,
      "endTime": 49.384174346900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5783468247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "こころはまた莉央さんをからかって……\n失礼なこと言っちゃダメだってば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ you’re teasing Rio-san again…\nYou shouldn't say something rude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5783468247,
      "endTime": 55.3654898644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.5596623421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "あれがこころなりの愛情表現なのは分かってるよ\n愛も、僕のことをからかってくれてもいいんだけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that’s Kokoro’s way of showing affection.\nAi‚ you can tease me too‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5596623421,
      "endTime": 62.855535316499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.0596623421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな恐れ多いこと、私にはムリですよ～！\nお二人とも永遠の憧れなんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I couldn’t possibly do something so disrespectful~!\nYou two are my eternal idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0596623421,
      "endTime": 70.50428800590001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.6984604836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんだって、同じリズノワの一員じゃないですか\n相変わらず、奥ゆかしいというか、なんというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan‚ you’re a member of LizNoir too‚ you know.\nYou’re still so modest‚ or whatever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6984604836,
      "endTime": 78.3926779747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.5868504524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "その点、こころは常にセンターの座を狙ってますから\nこのこころこそが、明日のリズノワを引っ張る――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that regard‚ Kokoro is always aiming for the center position.\nSo‚ Kokoro is the one who will lead LizNoir into the future――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5868504524,
      "endTime": 87.4922926903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5864636421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "こころのいつもの冗談はともかく\n僕達は四人になってから随分成長したと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting aside Kokoro’s usual jokes‚\nI think we've grown a lot since we became a four-member group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5864636421,
      "endTime": 95.20651054380001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3864656766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "それは今回のライブツアーの出来でも\nみんな、実感してるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we could all see that in the results\nof this live tour‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3864656766,
      "endTime": 100.0344247182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.21979901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんはつれないですけど、言ってることには同感です\nそろそろ、目に見える結果が欲しいところですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san is being cold‚ but I agree with what she’s saying.\nIt’s about time we see some tangible results~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.21979901,
      "endTime": 108.9020440738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.0962165515
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "目に見える結果？\n観客動員数とか、新曲の順位ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tangible results?\nYou mean like audience numbers or the ranking of our new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0962165515,
      "endTime": 114.66115967440001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.8553321521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "ブブー。ハズレです。こころ達にとっての一番の結果\nそれはVENUSプログラムのランキングですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bzzt‚ wrong. The best result for us\nis the VENUS program rankings!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8553321521,
      "endTime": 123.53496891660001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7291413943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルとは、ランキング一位のこと\nそのためには、まずBIG4にならないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A top idol is someone who ranks first‚\nand to achieve that‚ we need to become BIG4 first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7291413943,
      "endTime": 130.8403205553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0344930331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私達がBIG4かぁ……なれるのかなぁ……\nううん、なるんだ！　……なれます、よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Us‚ becoming BIG4… I wonder if we can do it…\nMhm‚ we will! …We can do it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0344930331,
      "endTime": 141.0588925997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.3476131969
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.2530650775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。なれるよ。僕達はランキング十位以内の\n常連だからね。もうとっくに射程圏内だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll be fine. We can do it. We’re always in the top ten\nof the rankings. We’re already within range.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2530650775,
      "endTime": 149.587373511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7863984108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。でもまだBIG4の座に届いていないのも事実\nもっと頑張らないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. But it’s also true that we haven’t reached BIG4 yet.\nWe need to work harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
