      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみにその仕事、断っても大丈夫なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ is it okay to refuse this job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.0003255604,
      "endTime": 341.54184477309997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、リズノワのみんなの意見を尊重する\n嫌なら無理に受ける必要はないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we’ll respect LizNoir’s decision.\nIf you don’t want to do it‚ you don’t have to force yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.7336588937,
      "endTime": 347.8394641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと葵さ～ん、こんないい話を断るなんて何\n考えてるんですか？　莉央さんもなんか言って下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ wait‚ Aoi-san~‚ what are you thinking‚\nrefusing such a great offer? Rio-san‚ say something!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.0336588937,
      "endTime": 357.7706429558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "やりましょう、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's do it‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.9648154336,
      "endTime": 359.83726893249997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、ぜひともやるべき――\nって、莉央さんは莉央さんで即答！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ we should definitely do it――\nWait‚ Rio-san‚ you’re agreeing immediately!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.0314414102,
      "endTime": 365.148969658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "普段なら「もっと慎重に」とか言うのに……\n自分で聞いといてなんですけど、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’d usually say “Let’s be more careful” or something…\nI’m the one who asked you‚ but are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.3431421357,
      "endTime": 372.22044363789996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10523.529617199983
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "確かに不安要素はあるのかもしれない\n資料もよく見ると、『詳細は口頭で』って記載が多いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll admit there might be some cause for concern.\nIf you look closely at the materials‚ there’s a lot of “Details to be discussed verbally.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.4146161156,
      "endTime": 380.520468052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけで\nこんなにいい話を蹴るのはもったいないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But just because of that‚\nit would be a waste to turn down such a good offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 380.7146405297,
      "endTime": 384.9871489601,
      "sfxList": []
