      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "私達のさらなる飛躍のきっかけになるかもしれない\nだから、やりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This could be an opportunity for us to make a further leap forward.\nSo‚ let’s do it.",
